data.description: Beautiful Mid-Century modern home! Well cared for and updated. Two main bedrooms with en-suites. 5 bedroom 3 bath home all on one level perfectly nestled on the edge of a cul-de-sac street in an established mid century subdivision with beautiful grown trees all around! The most recent updates include; Custom kitchen with large pullout drawers and loads of cabinets. New carpet. Newer paint inside and out. Newer 50 year roof. updated bathrooms and solid countertops. Over sized garage. New garage doors. Insulated heating ducks, special window shades and solar light tubes provide lower than average utility bills! Centrally located and close to schools, library, parks, freeway access and shopping. Large drive way with separate concrete pad with waste dump portal on the back side of the property for RV or more parking. Enclosed backyard, garden area, covered pergola and two storage sheds! Water is Capital Water with vary Low Rates! You are going to LOVE this home and location! Seller's 2.25%VA  loan is assumable!
